---
const team = [
  { name: 'Alex Chen', role: 'CEO & Co-founder', initials: 'AC' },
  { name: 'Sarah Kim', role: 'CTO & Co-founder', initials: 'SK' },
  { name: 'Marcus Johnson', role: 'Head of Design', initials: 'MJ' },
  { name: 'Priya Patel', role: 'Head of Engineering', initials: 'PP' },
];
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">About Diva</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We started Diva in 2025 with a simple mission: make it easy for teams to build beautiful,
        performant web pages without reinventing the wheel every time.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our component library combines the power of Astro with the elegance of shadcn/ui, giving you
        a production-ready design system that scales from landing pages to full-featured
        applications.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Our Team</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {
          team.map((member) => (
            <div class="border-border bg-card flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="bg-primary/10 text-primary flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
                {member.initials}
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">{member.name}</p>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">{member.role}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="border-border bg-card rounded-xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Simplicity</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 text-sm">
            We believe great design is invisible. Every component should feel natural.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-border bg-card rounded-xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 text-sm">
            Zero JS by default. Your pages should load in milliseconds, not seconds.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-border bg-card rounded-xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Accessibility</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 text-sm">
            Every component follows WAI-ARIA standards. The web should work for everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-border bg-card rounded-xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Openness</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 text-sm">
            Built with open source tools. No lock-in, no black boxes, full transparency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
